@startuml
title Viaverse Translation / Regional Config — State Diagram

[*] --> MISSING
MISSING --> DRAFT : create
DRAFT --> IN_REVIEW : submit
IN_REVIEW --> PUBLISHED : approve
IN_REVIEW --> DRAFT : changes requested
PUBLISHED --> FALLBACK_ACTIVE : target locale missing
FALLBACK_ACTIVE --> PUBLISHED : translation available
PUBLISHED --> DEPRECATED : key retired
DEPRECATED --> ARCHIVED : cleanup

[*] --> REGIONAL_CONFIG_DRAFT
REGIONAL_CONFIG_DRAFT --> REGIONAL_CONFIG_PUBLISHED : approve config
REGIONAL_CONFIG_PUBLISHED --> REGIONAL_CONFIG_DRAFT : new version

ARCHIVED --> [*]

note bottom
Publishing translation/regional config should be versioned and rollbackable.
SEO localized slugs need canonical/hreflang consistency before publish.
end note
@enduml
